BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:B517uGJq5ANsd4BaebwkC
SUMMARY:Insider’s Breakfast and Culture Tour of Pike Place Market
DTSTAMP:20260327T070520Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260604T180000
DESCRIPTION:VOTED 10 BEST FOOD TOURS IN THE COUNTRY BY USA TODAY! Get ahead
	 of peak crowds and join Savor Seattle as they take you behind the scenes 
	on an early-morning exploration of Pike Place Market. Their guides on this
	 tour are deeply rooted members of the Market community who will truly tak
	e you to “Meet The Producer” using their years of experience in the neighb
	orhood. This is an experience you cannot get with any regular tour guide! 
	Feel like a local as you walk and eat your way through the best morning bi
	tes! Learn the names and stories of the people who operate the businesses 
	Seattle Savor's is honored to highlight as their guides give you the full 
	history of how Pike Place became The Soul of Seattle. "Watching the Market
	 come to life is a time-honored Seattle tradition we would love for you to
	 witness as we share our years of expertise with you. Come savor mornings 
	at Pike Place Market!" Tours are available on Monday\, Thursday\, Friday\,
	 Saturday and Sunday from 8am - 10:30pm Book a Tour \n\nhttps://www.pikepl
	acemarket.org/events-calendar/insiders-breakfast-and-culture-tour-of-pike-
	place-market/?occurrence=2026-03-27\n\nFrom Pike Place Market Events
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/insiders-breakfast-and-
	culture-tour-of-pike-place-market/?occurrence=2026-03-27
LOCATION:Pike Place Market
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:events
CATEGORIES:Pike Place Market Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT14H30M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:IPH_jFYQh-mTVdAZAFIOr
SUMMARY:The Original Food and Culture Tour of Pike Place Market
DTSTAMP:20260327T070520Z
DTSTART:20260327T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:VOTED 10 BEST FOOD TOURS IN THE COUNTRY BY USA TODAY! Join Savo
	r Seattle for Seattle’s original food and cultural tour of Pike Place Mark
	et! On their signature tour\, they will take you on a journey through the 
	lively and bustling days in the heart of Seattle: Pike Place Market. While
	 their guides give you the most delicious tastings at eight different part
	ners. You’ll also learn the history of the Market and hear the stories of 
	the small-batch food and craft producers that make this place one of Seatt
	le’s most beloved landmarks. Find out why fish fly\, why a pig is our masc
	ot\, how the “Original” Starbucks was founded\, how an alleyway became cov
	ered in gum\, what made Pike Place Market one of Anthony Bourdain’s favori
	te places\, and many more pieces of info Seattle Savor guides we’ll be thr
	illed to share with you while you savor culinary offerings. Once you’re do
	ne\, you’ll be equipped and ready to dive deeper into the historic neighbo
	rhood. Tours are available daily\, starting at 10am and 2\n\nhttps://www.p
	ikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/the-original-food-and-culture-tour-of-p
	ike-place-market/?occurrence=2026-03-27\n\nFrom Pike Place Market Events
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/the-original-food-and-c
	ulture-tour-of-pike-place-market/?occurrence=2026-03-27
LOCATION:Pike Place Market
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:events
CATEGORIES:Pike Place Market Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:wxf-tAd_od5EiTSdn99Di
SUMMARY:Improv Happy Hour
DTSTAMP:20260327T070520Z
DTSTART:20260327T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Improv Happy Hour—where comedy is unscripted\, unpr
	edictable\, and unbelievably fun! From movie mashups to literary spoofs an
	d bold\, experimental comedy\, our quick-thinking performers turn your sug
	gestions into hilarious scenes on the spot. This family-friendly show at t
	he iconic Gum Wall in Pike Place Market guarantees a night of laughter\, s
	urprises\, and improv magic you won’t forget. Bring your wildest ideas\, y
	our loudest laughs\, and get ready for a one-of-a-kind comedy experience—b
	ecause at Improv Happy Hour\, anything can happen (and usually does)! Buy 
	Tickets\n\nhttps://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/improv-happy-ho
	ur-2/?occurrence=2026-03-27\n\nFrom Pike Place Market Events
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/improv-happy-hour-2/?oc
	currence=2026-03-27
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:events
CATEGORIES:Pike Place Market Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:zFEn5ios3iGnTHPgd6ZGq
SUMMARY:An Evening with Stephanie Anne Johnson
DTSTAMP:20260327T070520Z
DTSTART:20260327T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Rabbit Box is excited to present An Evening with Stephanie 
	Anne Johnson \, accompanied by Jeff Fielder . They will perform two sets: 
	One set will be the new album ‘Sing\, baby!’ performed in its entirety. Th
	e second set will all be cover songs\; some you’ve never heard Stephanie p
	erform before! Pacific Northwest Americana songwriter and performer Stepha
	nie Anne Johnson ’ s (they/them) voice is like a prayer. It’s the kind of 
	sound that makes you feel renewed\, refreshed\, and in love with the highe
	r spirits of the planet. It’s a sound you can bask in\, that can wash over
	 you and regenerate the best of you all at once. And they have wowed judge
	s on the immensely popular NBC TV series\, The Voice\, showcasing their gi
	fts. Buy Tickets\n\nhttps://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/an-eve
	ning-with-stephanie-anne-johnson/?occurrence=2026-03-27\n\nFrom Pike Place
	 Market Events
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/an-evening-with-stephan
	ie-anne-johnson/?occurrence=2026-03-27
LOCATION:The Rabbit Box\, 94 Pike Street Unit 11
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:events
CATEGORIES:Pike Place Market Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:fFdn1rd4e-P04cbH8ANEr
SUMMARY:Seattle Suites: An Improvised Neil Simon Comedy
DTSTAMP:20260327T070520Z
DTSTART:20260327T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Improvised comedy in the style of Neil Simon\\\, where one hote
	l suite becomes a comedic pressure cooker for 3 hilarious improvised tales
	\\n\\n\\n\\nOne hotel suite. Countless misunderstandings. Relentless laugh
	s. \\nSeattle Suite is a laugh-driven\\\, fully improvised play inspired b
	y the style of Plaza Suite and California Suite\\\, capturing the signatur
	e humor of Neil Simon that is fast\\\, verbal\\\, and rooted in beautifull
	y human flaws. Each night\\\, a single Seattle hotel room becomes the sett
	ing for interconnected scenes inspired by your suggestions\\\, friends ove
	rshare and spiral\\\, romantic gestures go wrong\\\, awkward silences stre
	tch\\\, and small problems become big ones. The comedy comes from characte
	r and relationship\\\, building through sharp dialogue\\\, escalating tens
	ion\\\, and recognizable\\\, lived-in situations. Perfect for fans of smar
	t comedy\\\, relationship humor\\\, and classic theatrical wit.\n\nhttps:/
	/www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-suites-an-improvised-neil-sim
	on-comedy/2026-03-27/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-suites-an-improvise
	d-neil-simon-comedy/2026-03-27/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:ypGm0ImbArSU-vN5oVpTF
SUMMARY:Seattle Theatresports 2026
DTSTAMP:20260327T070520Z
DTSTART:20260327T213000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle’s high-energy improv battle where your suggestions shap
	e every scene. Fast\\\, funny\\\, unpredictable comedy Fri. & Sat. 9:30\\n
	\\n\\n\\nWelcome to Seattle’s funnest improv comedy show\\\, a high-energy
	\\\, no-rules showdown where your ideas shape every scene. Seattle Theatre
	sports at Unexpected Productions’ Market Theater in Pike Place Market is p
	art comedy battle\\\, part game night\\\, and completely powered by the cr
	owd. Boo the judges. Cheer the Gum Wall race and laugh til it hurts! \\nEv
	ery show\\\, two teams of top Seattle improvisers go head to head\\\, perf
	orming games\\\, stories\\\, characters\\\, and scenes inspired entirely b
	y your suggestions. Judges score the rounds\\\, decide the winners\\\, and
	 shape the fun (as we boo them). No scripts. No safety nets. Just fast thi
	nking\\\, bold choices\\\, and pure creative mayhem. \\nThis isn’t your pa
	rents’ improv show\\\, unless your parents were super cool.\n\nhttps://www
	.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-theatresports-2026-test/2026-03-2
	7/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-theatresports-2026-
	test/2026-03-27/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
